e7b6019f627a898ecca592f3a18dcbb5a4ac116e.name: post
e7b6019f627a898ecca592f3a18dcbb5a4ac116e.source:
query post($id: Int!) {
  searchReviewRoom(roomId: $id) {
    __typename
    id
    createdAt
    updatedAt
    review {
      __typename
      id
      createdAt
      updatedAt
      title
      content
      upload
      userId
      placeId
      getLikes
      getUnLikes
      isLike
      isUnLike
      comments {
        __typename
        id
        userId
        createdAt
        updatedAt
        payload
      }
    }
  }
}

a97d11151162da16fc32dccdc23a540a9660d08c.name: searchPlace
a97d11151162da16fc32dccdc23a540a9660d08c.source:
query searchPlace($title: String!, $category: String, $lastID: Int) {
  searchPlace(title: $title, category: $category, lastId: $lastID) {
    __typename
    id
    createdAt
    updatedAt
    title
    address
    zipCode
    x
    y
    category
  }
}

863d54afe03a509a7507a65632f9ba036e8cdda6.name: searchReview
863d54afe03a509a7507a65632f9ba036e8cdda6.source:
query searchReview($title: String, $category: String, $lastID: Int) {
  searchReview(title: $title, category: $category, lastId: $lastID) {
    __typename
    id
    createdAt
    updatedAt
    title
    content
    upload
    userId
    placeId
    getLikes
    getUnLikes
    isLike
    isUnLike
    user {
      __typename
      id
    }
    comments {
      __typename
      id
      createdAt
      updatedAt
      payload
      reviewId
    }
    errorCode
  }
}

82fedfbfbf51c5b207939d62c9cc80766e7d08d6.name: seeProfile
82fedfbfbf51c5b207939d62c9cc80766e7d08d6.source:
query seeProfile($userName: String!) {
  seeProfile(userName: $userName) {
    __typename
    id
    userName
    nickName
    email
    avatar
    bio
    gender
    ageRanger
    createdAt
    updatedAt
    platformType
  }
}
